Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:11.99,main,Hinata,0,0,0,,Ninja kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:15.46,main,Hinata,0,0,0,,Các cậu thấy chứ? Ninja đó! Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.51,main,Hinata,0,0,0,,Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:17.51,main,Hana,0,0,0,,Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:26.73,main,Hinata,0,0,0,,Nin! Nin! Nin! Nin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:29.49,main,Hinata,0,0,0,,Đỡ lấy, đồ xấu xa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:30.89,main,Hana,0,0,0,,Cậu ấy đang làm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.64,top,Hinata,0,0,0,,Đỡ- Đỡ- Đỡ lấy nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.04,main,Noa,0,0,0,,Làm gì giờ, Hana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:37.97,main,Hana,0,0,0,,Tụi mình cũng qua đó nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:39.41,main,Noa,0,0,0,,Ư-Ừ... ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:43.61,main,Noa,0,0,0,,Mồ, bó tay Hinata-chan thật mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.82,sign_5362_50_The_Theater_Club,sign,0,0,0,,Câu lạc bộ nhạc kịch xin trân trọng giới thiệu\N{\fs33}Biệt đội Ninja\N{\fs27}~ Phần 6 ~
