Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.06,main,Noa,0,0,0,,Ô, vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.57,main,Hana,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn chị rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.53,main,Hinata,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn chị nha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:05.58,main,Miyako,0,0,0,,Are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.39,main,Miyako,0,0,0,,Tại sao các em lại ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:08.49,main,Hinata,0,0,0,,Mya-nee!
