Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:27.56,main,Miyako,0,0,0,,Giảng viên của chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:28.79,main,Noa,0,0,0,,Chào cô ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.27,main,teacher,0,0,0,,Chào các em.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:31.68,main,teacher,0,0,0,,Hoshino-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:34.32,main,teacher,0,0,0,,Bài làm của em tốt đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.20,main,Miyako,0,0,0,,Hở?
