Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.31,italics,Miyako,0,0,0,,Đột nhập à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.24,sign_18372_280_Escape,sign; bottom,0,0,0,,Bỏ chạy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:51.24,sign_18372_277_Report,sign; right,0,0,0,,{\c&H8CA37A&}Báo C.A
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.24,sign_18372_283_Fight,sign; left,0,0,0,,Chiến đấu
